parent1.code: A watercolor of a golden phoenix with radiant feathers in the style of abstract expressionism. It perches on the edge of a craggy cliff overlooking a vast desert under a twilight sky, casting a warm glow from its wings, amidst a landscape of wind-carved rock formations and floating glass orbs.

offspring.code: A watercolor of a resplendent golden phoenix with magnificent radiant feathers in the style of vibrant abstract expressionism. It elegantly perches on the rugged edge of a craggy cliff overlooking a vast, serene desert under a stunning twilight sky, casting an enchanting warm glow from its wings, amidst a surreal landscape of towering wind-carved rock formations and mesmerizing floating glass orbs.
